Package com.company

Class Borrow

java.lang.Object
com.company.Borrow
public class Borrow
extends java.lang.Object
Borrow class represents a borrow in a library system. It holds a user, a book, a dead line date and current date as issued date.
Author:
Fatemeh Valeh
